Welcome to mm, the MinuteMailer for benedikt.rumpf@caroobi.com

Options are:

w:        Add  topics you worked on

r:        Add Roadblocks you might encounter

o:        Add Observations during the day

t:        Add your Thoughts

f:        Add your Feelings

c:        check the current status of the MinuteMail

d:        Opens your MinuteMail. You can now either edit or send the mail

s:        Sends your MinuteMail directly without editing or displaying

remind:   Opens another terminal and closes it right after the interation.
          Similar to done.

help:     display this file

reset:    Resets the MinuteMail so that you can start from scratch.
          It is reset automatically afer each send

test:     Sends a testmail to the address specified
